## 🚀 What is Innovate CLI?

**Innovate CLI** is your AI-powered code agent that turns prompts into fully functional projects.

- 🧠 **Driven by Gemini 1.5 Flash**  
- 🏗️ Creates complete project structures with commands, file creation & execution  
- 📁 Auto-organizes projects into unique folders  
- 💬 CLI and Flask-based GUI support  
- 📜 Every file is auto-branded with credit  
- 📝 Uses a clear, minimal instruction format

***

## 🔧 CLI in Action

```bash
$ python cli.py
Welcome to Innovate CLI 0.3!
> Powered by Gemini.
> Built by AI, to AI, from AI and for AI.

What do you want to build or do? 
> Make a portfolio site with Next.js and Tailwind

📁 Working in project folder: projects/project_20250716_abcd1
📋 Generated Raw Output:
[CD] portfolio
[CMD] npx create-next-app@latest .
...
